config.title: Call volume for a large North American bank

info:
callsR Documentation

Call volume for a large North American bank

Description

Five-minute call volume handled on weekdays between 7:00am and 9:05pm, beginning 3 March 2003 for 164 days.

Format

Time series object of class msts.

Source

Rob Hyndman

Examples


autoplot(calls, xlab="Weeks")
